    <dashboard name='Story 1' type='storyboard'>
      <layout-options>
        <title>
          <formatted-text>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='-webkit-standard'>Æ              </run>
          </formatted-text>
        </title>
      </layout-options>
      <style>
        <style-rule element='story-point-caption'>
          <format attr='width' value='139' />
        </style-rule>
      </style>
      <size maxheight='964' maxwidth='1616' minheight='964' minwidth='1616' sizing-mode='fixed' />
      <zones>
        <zone h='100000' id='2' type-v2='layout-basic' w='100000' x='0' y='0'>
          <zone h='98340' id='7' param='vert' removable='false' type-v2='layout-flow' w='99010' x='495' y='830'>
            <zone h='3838' id='8' type-v2='title' w='99010' x='495' y='830'>
              <zone-style>
                <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
                <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
                <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
                <format attr='margin' value='4' />
              </zone-style>
            </zone>
            <zone h='94502' id='1' param='vert' removable='false' type-v2='layout-flow' w='99010' x='495' y='4668'>
              <zone h='10477' id='4' is-fixed='true' paired-zone-id='5' removable='false' type-v2='flipboard-nav' w='99010' x='495' y='4668' />
              <zone h='84025' id='5' paired-zone-id='4' removable='false' type-v2='flipboard' w='99010' x='495' y='15145'>
                <flipboard active-id='13' nav-type='caption' show-nav-arrows='true'>
                  <story-points>
                    <story-point caption='Overview' captured-sheet='Dashboard 1' id='3' />
                    <story-point caption='Total Response' captured-sheet='Total Response' id='4' />
                    <story-point caption='Who took the survey?' captured-sheet='Age Group' id='5' />
                    <story-point caption='Digital Payment Habits' captured-sheet='Payment Frequency' id='6' />
                    <story-point caption='Crypto Awareness' captured-sheet='Crypto awareness' id='7' />
                    <story-point caption='Understanding Gap' captured-sheet='Crypto Understanding' id='8' />
                    <story-point caption='Adoption Willingness' captured-sheet='Crypto Adoption' id='9' />
                    <story-point caption='Top Barriers' captured-sheet='Top Barriers' id='10' />
                    <story-point caption='Support Needed' captured-sheet='Suppoprt needed' id='11' />
                    <story-point caption='Readiness by Area&#10;&#10;' captured-sheet='Readiness Score by Area' id='12' />
                    <story-point caption='Bhutan overall Readiness' captured-sheet='Bhutan Readiness' id='13' />
                  </story-points>
                </flipboard>
              </zone>
            </zone>
          </zone>
          <zone-style>
            <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
            <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
            <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
            <format attr='margin' value='8' />
          </zone-style>
        </zone>
        <zone flipboard-zone-id='5' forceUpdate='true' h='17739' hidden='true' id='9' story-point-id='3' type-v2='text' w='90408' x='743' y='65664'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' lmargin='600' rmargin='600'>I am interested in this project because Bhutan is at a unique turning point. With ambitious developments like Gelephu Mindfulness City on the horizon, digital finance is no longer a distant concept - it is becoming a real opportunity for our country. As a Business Intelligence student interning at Bhutan Data Scientists, I wanted to contribute something meaningful by answering a question - are people in Bhutan actually ready for cryptocurrency?</run>
            <run fontalignment='0' lmargin='600' rmargin='600'>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' lmargin='600' rmargin='600'>What makes this personally interesting to me is that readiness is not just about technology. It is about trust, awareness and confidence. I wanted to understand the real human side of this - what do ordinary Bhutanese people feel, fear and hope for when it comes to digital finance. This project gave me the chance to combine my data skills with something that genuinely matters for Bhutan&apos;s future.</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
        <zone flipboard-zone-id='5' forceUpdate='true' h='5602' hidden='true' id='10' story-point-id='4' type-v2='text' w='37686' x='5941' y='42531'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run>A data was collected from 113 people whose age group is above 18.</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
        <zone flipboard-zone-id='5' h='3112' hidden='true' id='11' story-point-id='5' type-v2='text' w='27723' x='27351' y='82469'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='-webkit-standard'>18-24 Year Olds Dominate - Mostly from Urban Areas</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
        <zone flipboard-zone-id='5' h='3112' hidden='true' id='12' story-point-id='6' type-v2='text' w='30260' x='46906' y='72822'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='-webkit-standard'>Most Respondents Already Use Digital Payments Regularly</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
        <zone flipboard-zone-id='5' h='3112' hidden='true' id='13' story-point-id='7' type-v2='text' w='27042' x='51609' y='67842'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='-webkit-standard'>96% of Respondents Have Heard of Cryptocurrency</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
        <zone flipboard-zone-id='5' h='3112' hidden='true' id='14' story-point-id='8' type-v2='text' w='27290' x='29889' y='65041'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='-webkit-standard'>Awareness is High But Understanding Remains Basic</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
        <zone flipboard-zone-id='5' h='3112' hidden='true' id='15' story-point-id='9' type-v2='text' w='30507' x='48020' y='54876'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='-webkit-standard'>Majority Are Willing to Adopt Crypto With the Right Support</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
        <zone flipboard-zone-id='5' h='3112' hidden='true' id='16' story-point-id='10' type-v2='text' w='27847' x='1052' y='31535'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='-webkit-standard'>Poor Internet is the Biggest Barrier to Crypto Adoption</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
        <zone flipboard-zone-id='5' h='6017' hidden='true' id='17' story-point-id='11' type-v2='text' w='36572' x='30879' y='48963'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run fontsize='16'>Better Internet and Training are the most requested support.</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
        <zone flipboard-zone-id='5' forceUpdate='true' h='7469' hidden='true' id='18' story-point-id='12' type-v2='text' w='47772' x='3713' y='34751'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='-webkit-standard'>Semi-Urban Middle-Aged Groups Lead Crypto Readiness — Urban Elderly Score Lowest out of 16.</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
        <zone flipboard-zone-id='5' forceUpdate='true' h='4772' id='19' story-point-id='13' type-v2='text' w='39233' x='28713' y='90871'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='-webkit-standard'>59% of Respondents Believe Bhutan is Somewhat Ready for Digital Finance.</run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
      </zones>
      <simple-id uuid='{C38FBD78-BBB0-4BC2-A4E7-CAEA20359375}' />
    </dashboard>
    <dashboard name='Story 2' type='storyboard'>
      <style />
      <size sizing-mode='automatic' />
      <zones>
        <zone h='100000' id='2' type-v2='layout-basic' w='100000' x='0' y='0'>
          <zone h='98144' id='10' param='vert' removable='false' type-v2='layout-flow' w='98932' x='534' y='928'>
            <zone h='98144' id='1' param='vert' removable='false' type-v2='layout-flow' w='98932' x='534' y='928'>
              <zone h='11717' id='4' is-fixed='true' paired-zone-id='5' removable='false' type-v2='flipboard-nav' w='98932' x='534' y='928' />
              <zone h='86427' id='5' paired-zone-id='4' removable='false' type-v2='flipboard' w='98932' x='534' y='12645'>
                <flipboard active-id='4' nav-type='caption' show-nav-arrows='true'>
                  <story-points>
                    <story-point caption='Overview' captured-sheet='' id='1' />
                    <story-point caption='Young Bhutanese Learn Fast - But Knowledge Gaps Remain' captured-sheet='GNH Education' id='2' />
                    <story-point caption='Digital Familiarity Shows Improving Financial Access Across Bhutan.' captured-sheet='GNH Living Standards' id='3' />
                    <story-point caption='Fear of Scams is the Silent Barrier -Trust Must Come Before Technology' captured-sheet='GNH Psychological wellbeing' id='4' />
                    <story-point caption='Urban Communities Lead -Rural Bhutan Must Not Be Left Behind' captured-sheet='GNH Community Vtality' id='5' />
                    <story-point caption='Digital Payments Already Saving Time - Crypto is the Natural Next Step&quot;' captured-sheet='GNH Time use' id='6' />
                    <story-point caption='People Are Asking For Leadership - Government Must Invest in Internet and Training' captured-sheet='GNH Governance' id='7' />
                  </story-points>
                </flipboard>
              </zone>
            </zone>
          </zone>
          <zone-style>
            <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
            <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
            <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
            <format attr='margin' value='8' />
          </zone-style>
        </zone>
        <zone flipboard-zone-id='5' forceUpdate='true' h='86936' hidden='true' id='8' story-point-id='1' type-v2='text' w='98999' x='334' y='9942'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run bold='true' fontsize='20'>Cryptocurrency Readiness as a GNH Story 🇧🇹</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run fontsize='16'>B</run>
            <run>hutan measures progress through happiness -
not just money. While other countries ask 
&quot;Is crypto profitable?&quot; - Bhutan asks 
&quot;Is crypto good for our people?&quot;

This story maps cryptocurrency readiness 
across 6 GNH domains:

🎓 Education
🏠 Living Standards  
🧠 Psychological Wellbeing
🏛️ Governance
🤝 Community Vitality
⏰ Time Use

Each domain tells a different part of 
Bhutan&apos;s crypto readiness story.</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
        <zone flipboard-zone-id='5' forceUpdate='true' h='14451' hidden='true' id='11' story-point-id='2' type-v2='text' w='39760' x='33889' y='65896'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run>18-24 year olds score highest at 3.14 out of 4 
- but understanding drops sharply with age. 
55+ score only 1.83. Bhutan needs more
crypto education for older generations.</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
        <zone flipboard-zone-id='5' forceUpdate='true' h='14682' hidden='true' id='12' story-point-id='3' type-v2='text' w='36157' x='47165' y='59306'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run>Most respondents are somewhat to very familiar 
with digital tools - showing improving living 
standards and financial access across Bhutan. 
Better digital access means better quality of life.</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
        <zone flipboard-zone-id='5' forceUpdate='true' h='20578' id='13' story-point-id='4' type-v2='text' w='31821' x='32155' y='40000'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run>Older age groups show higher security concern 
- 45-54 scoring 4.64 out of 5. Fear of scams 
and losing money is the silent barrier to 
crypto adoption. Trust must be built before 
technology can succeed in Bhutan.</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
        <zone flipboard-zone-id='5' h='15491' hidden='true' id='14' story-point-id='5' type-v2='text' w='29887' x='31621' y='65202'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run>Urban communities show the highest adoption 
willingness with 76 respondents. Rural and 
Semi-Urban communities must not be left behind. 
Crypto adoption in Bhutan will only succeed 
if it reaches every community equally.</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
        <zone flipboard-zone-id='5' forceUpdate='true' h='18728' hidden='true' id='15' story-point-id='6' type-v2='text' w='30420' x='35090' y='64855'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run>Urban residents use digital payments most 
frequently - saving time on banking and cash 
handling. This habit shows Bhutanese people 
are already comfortable with digital finance. 
Cryptocurrency is simply the next step in 
that time saving journey.</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
        <zone flipboard-zone-id='5' h='18728' hidden='true' id='16' story-point-id='7' type-v2='text' w='38826' x='33756' y='35029'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run>Better Internet leads with 77 respondents 
requesting it as top support. Training programs 
follow closely with 73. Government Support 
received only 1 direct mention - but people 
expect leadership through infrastructure 
and education investment.</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
      </zones>
      <simple-id uuid='{E55877AB-153F-47DE-82ED-2656298819FD}' />
    </dashboard>
    <dashboard name='Story 3' type='storyboard'>
      <style />
      <size maxheight='964' maxwidth='1016' minheight='964' minwidth='1016' />
      <zones>
        <zone h='100000' id='2' type-v2='layout-basic' w='100000' x='0' y='0'>
          <zone h='98340' id='1' param='vert' removable='false' type-v2='layout-flow' w='98426' x='787' y='830'>
            <zone h='3423' id='3' type-v2='title' w='98426' x='787' y='830' />
            <zone h='10477' id='4' is-fixed='true' paired-zone-id='5' removable='false' type-v2='flipboard-nav' w='98426' x='787' y='4253' />
            <zone h='84440' id='5' paired-zone-id='4' removable='false' type-v2='flipboard' w='98426' x='787' y='14730'>
              <flipboard active-id='1' nav-type='caption' show-nav-arrows='true'>
                <story-points>
                  <story-point captured-sheet='' id='1' />
                </story-points>
              </flipboard>
            </zone>
          </zone>
          <zone-style>
